/**
 * English language pack — self-contained.
 *
 * Used in two ways at runtime:
 *   - As TARGET (user is learning English): the 'concepts' provide the
 *     English words shown in lesson chunks. The 'lesson_context' provides
 *     cultural notes about English-speaking culture, authored in English
 *     (source-of-truth) and translated lazily by Claude into the user's
 *     spoken language.
 *   - As NATIVE (user speaks English): the 'concepts' provide native-side
 *     translations in lesson chunks (the "easy" side of every bilingual
 *     pair). The 'ui_strings' drive the app chrome.
 *
 * Adding a new lesson = add concept_keys to the lesson_skeletons table +
 * add lesson_context entry here + add concept entries here for any new
 * concepts not already covered.
 */

